channel.title: I am stronger. - Thomaisho [Orchestral Electronic Fusion]
channel.description:
Hello again, I made this song as a response to the emotions I had directly after a heartbreaking moment. It’s warm, upbeat and soothing ^^
Please, take a listen, I hope you all enjoy: https://soundcloud.com/user-161462983/i-am-stronger
